      <title>芝加哥学校闹剧让信用评估人员警惕风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/chicago-schools-drama-catches-eye-of-credit-ratings-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会领导层的突然更迭引起了穆迪评级的注意，该公司表示，在学区面临越来越大的财务挑战之际，分析师正在关注这一情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/chicago-schools-drama-catches-eye-of-credit-ratings-companies</guid>
